# DeepFang v0.2.0

**Goliath Execution Isolation Stack** — three-stage sanitize → adjudicate → dispatch pipeline with hard Docker network isolation. Integrates with robofang, openclaude-mcp, and openmanus-mcp as a trusted execution sandbox.

[![Status: Salvage/Active](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Salvage%2FActive-orange.svg)](README.md)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)

> **Note (2026-05-04):** v0.1.0 was generated by DeepSeek V4 Pro and contained fictional container references (`ghcr.io/zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw:v0.7.4` — wrong product/nonexistent tag; `ghcr.io/openclaw/openclaw` — wrong product entirely). The supervisor, dashboard, DeepSeek bridge, and pipeline architecture are genuine and sound. v0.2.0 replaces the two fictional containers with custom implementations. See [SALVAGE_PLAN.md](docs/SALVAGE_PLAN.md) for the full analysis.

---

## Architecture

```
User / MCP Client / RoboFang / openclaude-mcp / openmanus-mcp
        │
        ▼
┌──────────────────────┐
│   Supervisor          │  FastAPI + FastMCP 3.2 SSE
│   Ports 10956/10957  │  React dashboard
└──────────┬───────────┘
           │
           ▼
┌──────────────────────┐
│   Sanitizer Shim      │  Custom Python/FastAPI
│   Port 10958          │  Reads configs/sanitizer/rules.yaml
│                       │  POST /sanitize → {allowed, threat_score, reason}
└──────────┬────────────┘
           │ allowed
           ▼
┌──────────────────────┐
│   DeepSeek Bridge     │  Custom Python/FastAPI (complete)
│   Port 10959          │  Proxies to DeepSeek cloud API
│                       │  POST /adjudicate → {verdict, rationale}
└──────────┬────────────┘
           │ approve only
           ▼
┌──────────────────────┐
│   Worker              │  Custom Python/FastAPI
│   Port 10960          │  Air-gapped (no WAN, Docker internal network)
│                       │  POST /execute → {success, output}
│                       │  Writes to /repos (d:/dev/repos bind-mount)
└──────────────────────┘
```

### Network Isolation

| Network | WAN | Services |
|---------|-----|----------|
| `deepfang-sanitize` | No | Sanitizer, Supervisor |
| `deepfang-adjudicate` | Yes | DeepSeek Bridge, Supervisor |
| `deepfang-worker` | **No (internal: true)** | Worker, Supervisor |
| `deepfang-internal` | No | Prometheus, Loki, Promtail, Grafana |

The worker's WAN isolation is enforced at the **Docker network layer**, not in software. Even a compromised worker cannot reach the internet.

### Port Map

| Service | Port | Purpose |
|---------|------|---------|
| Supervisor MCP + API | 10956 | FastMCP 3.2 SSE + FastAPI REST |
| Dashboard | 10957 | React web UI |
| Sanitizer Shim | 10958 | Custom sanitizer (replaces ZeroClaw fiction) |
| DeepSeek Bridge | 10959 | Adjudicator proxy to DeepSeek API |
| Worker | 10960 | Air-gapped executor (replaces OpenClaw fiction) |
| Prometheus | 10961 | Metrics |
| Loki | 10962 | Log aggregation |
| Grafana | 10963 | Observability |

